message.body: Ok I am going to move the first load of shit in tomorrow so I will leave you moola for my half of the Comcast and will pick up the peco bill to pay it.
Also I think you will be at work when I'm there (probs late morning/early afternoon) but wanted to warn you just in case you were walking around naked or something
Oh god. Well we will get very close this year I suppose
How is work treating you now that you're almost a week in?
Awesome. Bills are on the fridge. Yep I work 9-5. And I have definitely not bothered closing the bathroom door ever :P

I was planning to when you moved in dont worry haha :) it's good. Still learning but the girl I'm replacing is a good teacher and she is there for another two weeks. Also my boss from hell is in Israel until July so that makes it a bit easier I suppose
It is nice that you will probably feel more confident in yourself when she gets there then
Also I find dating infinitely stressful. Cant I just special order a significant other?
I hear there are some ways to do that but they may be ethically questionable...how are you doing with all of that btw?
I'm ok. It is good to have other okcers as a distraction
Also do we still need a garbage can? If we do I can buy and bring one tomorrow
Yep
Ok cool. Also any chance you could bring a car load of my stuff over to or place tomorrow? It would include a garbage can!
Sorry about the ugly chair in the living room. My sis insisted. We can throw it away as soon as she has forgotten about it
Sure!
Also you can fold up the green/purple chair if its in the way
Yay! Let me know when tomorrow works for you. Also I put $41 behind the bill on the fridge (instead of you giving be $3 for the peco bill I just took it out of my Comcast contribution).
Hey! I was wondering what your timing is for tomorrow so I can plan seeing Anna around being here to help you.
Whenever is good for you is good for me! Early maybe?
If I go stay at haverford is afternoon okay? I don't know if I will or not
Lizzyyyyy is afternoon okay?
Sure!
Let me know when you wanna come by
No I am packing shit now I just wanted to know when you were coming by
Are you waiting for me to start? We are leaving hc within 10 min.
Great
Ok cool. I will text when I am coming by
Text me before you head over here?
It probably won't be until late afternoon
But sure
Don't worry about it then :P
